&gt;&gt;Actually, he wasn’t a scientist of our time. He died before my time. I think Richard Feynman, Carl Sagan and Steven Hawkins are some of the most revered scientists of my time. It also doesn’t irk me one bit what he believed. I said before (and judging from your inability to agree on language will no doubt say again)<br>
